---
title: Shawarma-Inspired Double Chorizo Wraps with Crispy Shallots and Garlic Sauce
description: Chorizo sausage is seared with our Shawarma Spice Blend for a meal full of sweet and smoky aromas!  We've also got crunchy and tart pickled cabbage, as well as a bright herb and garlic sauce. All that's left to say is yum!

